# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../glossary.rst:23
msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "Rječnik"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../glossary.rst:25
msgid ""
"There is much technical terminology in today's fast-moving media-centric "
"world. If you find yourself wondering what a video production term or an "
"acronym means, you are certainly not alone. Like most industries, video "
"production has a language all its own. Here is a list of terms commonly "
"found in video editing. Becoming familiar with these terms only makes your "
"job easier."
msgstr ""
"U današnjem brzo mijenjajućem svijetu usmjerenom na medije postoji mnogo "
"tehničkih termina. Ako se pitate što neki pojam ili kratica u video "
"produkciji znači, niste sami. Kao i u većini industrija, video produkcija "
"ima svoj vlastiti jezik. Ovdje je popis pojmova koji se često nalaze u video "
"montaži. Upoznavanje s ovim pojmovima olakšava vaš posao."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../glossary.rst:34
msgid "Definitions"
msgstr "Definicije"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../glossary.rst:36
msgid ""
"These definitions are a work-in-progress. Please let us know if you need a "
"term defined by contacting support@openshot.org."
msgstr ""
"Ove definicije su u izradi. Javite nam ako vam treba definicija nekog pojma "
"kontaktiranjem support@openshot.org."

